OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine
OL,6,Fevening with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FOvernight, it will remain dry with
OL,8,Fclear spells. A little chilly in the
OL,9,Fcountryside but not as cold as recent
OL,10,Fnights. Potentially some mist and fog
OL,11,Fpatches developing near dawn in
OL,12,Fsheltered valleys.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FAnother settled day with
OL,15,Fsunshine for much of Wales. Possibly
OL,16,Fturning cloudier at times near
OL,17,Fnorthern and western coasts,
OL,18,Fpotentially developing into sea fog
OL,19,Flater. Feeling warm with light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
