OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FCooler and more changeable on
OL,7,FThursday, with spells of rain and
OL,8,Fshowers. Likely to stay unsettled on
OL,9,FFriday and Saturday with further rain
OL,10,Fat times, and temperatures nearer to
OL,11,Faverage.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
